# Athenaeum Credentials
ATHENAEUM_USERNAME=your_username_here
ATHENAEUM_PASSWORD=your_password_here

# Booking Configuration
# For weekly recurring bookings (used by GitHub Actions)
# Format: <DayName> <time HH:MM AM/PM>, comma separated
# Day names: Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday, Saturday, Sunday
BOOKING_LIST=Tuesday 7:00 PM,Wednesday 7:00 PM,Friday 4:00 PM,Sunday 10:00 AM

# Court to book: "both", "North Pickleball Court", or "South Pickleball Court"
# Set to "both" to book both North and South courts for each time slot
COURT_NAME=both
BOOKING_DURATION=120

# Legacy single booking parameters (for manual runs)
BOOKING_DATE=01/20/2026
BOOKING_TIME=10:00 AM

# Safety mode - set to false to actually complete booking
SAFETY_MODE=false

# Optional: Set to true to run without browser window
HEADLESS=false
```

## 5. Create .gitignore

Create `.gitignore` file:
```
# Environment variables (NEVER commit this!)
.env

# Python
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python

# Screenshots and output
*.png
*.html

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```

## 6. Project Structure

Your folder should look like this:
```
athenaeum-booking\
├── .env                      # Your secrets (NOT in git)
├── .env.example              # Template (safe for git)
├── .gitignore               # Protect secrets
├── athenaeum_booking.py     # Main script
├── venv\                    # Virtual environment
└── requirements.txt         # Dependencies (create this next)